
- Requirements:

  - CMake.

  - A C++ compiler with C++14 support.
    The following compiler has been tested:
    - GCC 5.4 (Linux x86_64).

- Build:

  - Linux - GCC:
    - Execute in a terminal (running bash):

      pkg_dir=$PWD
      mkdir ../gama_tts-build
      cd ../gama_tts-build
      cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release $pkg_dir
      make

  - Linux - LLVM/Clang:
    - Execute in a terminal (running bash):

      pkg_dir=$PWD
      mkdir ../gama_tts-build
      cd ../gama_tts-build
      CXX=clang++ cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release $pkg_dir
      make

- Install (Linux):

  # Optional:
  make install

- Test (Linux):

  ./gama_tts -c $pkg_dir/data/en -p /tmp/test_param.txt -o /tmp/test.wav "Hello world." && aplay -q /tmp/test.wav
